#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart/offload_kv_cache.rst:163
msgid "Example: CPU offloading benefits"
msgstr "示例：CPU 卸载的好处"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart/offload_kv_cache.rst:165
msgid ""
"This section demonstrates the performance benefits of using CPU "
"offloading with LMCache. We'll use a script that generates multiple "
"prompts and compare the performance with and without LMCache."
msgstr "本节演示了使用 CPU 卸载与 LMCache 结合的性能优势。我们将使用一个生成多个提示的脚本，并比较使用和不使用 LMCache 的性能。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart/offload_kv_cache.rst:168
msgid "Prerequisites (Setup)"
msgstr "前提条件（设置）"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart/offload_kv_cache.rst:170
msgid "A CUDA GPU. The example picks a model that fits the GPU automatically:"
msgstr "一块 CUDA GPU。示例会自动选择适合该 GPU 的模型："

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart/offload_kv_cache.rst:172
msgid ""
"``Qwen/Qwen3-8B`` (bf16) when the GPU has ~36 GiB or more (e.g. A100-80G,"
" H100)."
msgstr "``Qwen/Qwen3-8B`` (bf16) 当显存大约为 36 GiB 或更多时（例如 A100-80G, H100）。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart/offload_kv_cache.rst:173
msgid ""
"``Qwen/Qwen3-8B-FP8`` with ``kv_cache_dtype=\"fp8\"`` when the GPU has "
"~24 GiB and supports native FP8 (Ada Lovelace / Hopper, ``sm_89+``; e.g. "
"L4, L40, RTX 4090)."
msgstr "``Qwen/Qwen3-8B-FP8`` 与 ``kv_cache_dtype=\"fp8\"`` 当 GPU 具有约 24 GiB 并支持原生 FP8（Ada Lovelace / Hopper，``sm_89+``；例如 L4、L40、RTX 4090）。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart/offload_kv_cache.rst:175
msgid ""
"``Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B`` as the fallback for smaller GPUs (~10 GiB and up), "
"including Ampere 24 GiB cards (RTX A5000, RTX 3090) where FP8 is "
"unsupported."
msgstr "``Qwen/Qwen3-1.7B`` 作为较小显卡的后备选择（约 10 GiB 及以上），包括不支持 FP8 的安培 24 GiB 显卡（RTX A5000、RTX 3090）。"

#: ../../source/getting_started/quickstart/offload_kv_cache.rst:178
msgid ""
"Sufficient CPU memory. The example clamps the LMCache pinned host buffer "
"to fit your system RAM and ``RLIMIT_MEMLOCK`` (``ulimit -l``), so it also"
" works on smaller hosts without manual tuning."
msgstr "足够的 CPU 内存。该示例将 LMCache 固定主机缓冲区限制为适合您的系统 RAM 和 ``RLIMIT_MEMLOCK`` (``ulimit -l``)，因此它也可以在不进行手动调整的小型主机上运行。"

